title: Semiconducting Silicon Nanowires for Biomedical Applications
description:
English | 2014 | ISBN: 0857097660 | ISBN-13: 9780857097668 | 288 pages | PDF | 18,5 MB

Biomedical applications have benefited greatly from the increasing interest and research into semiconducting silicon nanowires. 

Semiconducting Silicon Nanowires for Biomedical Applications reviews the fabrication, properties, and applications of this emerging material.
